76,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"應該唔得 佢會叫你訂多晚酒店<br />\n我之前都試過 不過佢會按返比例收費<br />\n因為你始終唔係瞓足咁耐 我覺得可接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfdb4bc2527de5462dc9f5a715e74c5df95fea1","tid":399671,"uid":15136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"Book埋落機個晚咪得<br />\n又想訓又唔想比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4996f718fb66fa3c2861a0a0be71fa8aec6dc2","tid":399671,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"正常早check in 要收錢，你可以send email 問下酒店幾錢。<br />\n<br />\n另外我都成日搭凌晨4點班機到曼谷，係機場Hea 到有地鐵先出市區，around 6:30就已經去到酒店，放低行李係附近食個靚早餐。再Hea 到9點 去health land 按個泰式，或10點打後去其他舖做個spa 。"},{"pid":"08fd8a0b242422f89e1f6ff3cf187b33748ed0b2","tid":399671,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"有房既 多要收多d 錢 可能半日咁"}]}